div.div:
A 16-way preset selector FSM that selects a single
value for each of: index value, threshold value, and timer value.
This diagram is the full implementation of the
threshold_preset_sector FSM, differing in that the code
implements only states ST_0 to ST_9 and leaves room for
future implementation of ST_0 to ST_F. For this design to
function, it is a requirement that the input btn_chg_preset be
a one-shot pulse input.
